## 📌 User Stories

1. **Create Tasks**  
   As a user, I want to create tasks so that I can keep track of my work.

2. **Mark Tasks as Completed**  
   As a user, I want to mark tasks as completed so that I know what I’ve finished.

3. **View Tasks**  
   As a user, I want to view all my tasks in one place so that I can stay organized.

